data.description: QUALIFIES FOR ZERO DOWN Rural Development Loan! Welcome to the country in Greenwood! Sitting at the end of a street on over 1 acre you will find this precious farmhouse, ready for its' new owner! With a dreamy front porch and a gated backyard with SO much extra room for all your country needs. No restrictions! Did I mention the huge SHOP with electricity? This property has it all! Vinyl plank flooring inside with a new hot water heater...spacious bedrooms with a secluded master and walk in laundry or mud room. New tank on the water well with reverse osmosis. Book your showing today and don't miss out on this property with room to roam!
